WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:06.320
Why did the trend for wired headphones appear on the scene? Firstly, it's practicality.

2
00:00:06.320 --> 00:00:13.600
Wired headphones have outlasted the eras of bone pairs, CD-pairs, MP-3-pairs and still remain relevant.

3
00:00:13.600 --> 00:00:20.000
Secondly, it’s convenient; you don’t have to charge them every day, change the battery after a while, and so on.

4
00:00:20.000 --> 00:00:27.840
Thirdly, this is their speed of information transfer. Wired headphones have a much lower minimum latency than non-wired ones.

5
00:00:27.840 --> 00:00:33.600
Therefore, they are preferred by audiophiles, cyber athletes and musicians.

